\text{If we define the rings}\;\;\Bbb Z_n:=\Bbb Z/n\Bbb Z\;,\;n\in\Bbb N\;,\;\;\text{then the CRT tells us that}
\Bbb Z_n\times\Bbb Z_m\cong \Bbb Z_{(n,m)}\implies\Bbb Z_n^*\times\Bbb Z_m^*\cong \Bbb Z_{(n,m)}^*
\;|\Bbb Z_n^*|=\varphi(n)\;
